      <p>Continuous strategy, execution, and optimization under one structured framework for ongoing growth.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar">
      <h3>Milestone Structure</h3>
      <p>Every project follows a defined scope, timeline, and milestone structure. You stay informed at every stage.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar">
      <h3>No Hidden Costs</h3>
      <p>All projects operate on milestone-based or advance payment models with clear documentation and invoicing.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mission-block fade-in d2">
    <div class="section-label">Our Mission</div>
    <blockquote>
      "We help businesses build strong digital foundations — combining branding, content, marketing, and
      technology into <span>one cohesive growth system.</span>"
    </blockquote>
  </div>

  <div class="cta-wrap fade-in d3">
    <a href="/contact"   class="btn-primary">Get In Touch →</a>
    <a href="/portfolio" class="btn-ghost">View Portfolio</a>
  </div>

</section>

